    <title>Refugees contributor: Hein de Haas</title>
    <description>Hein de Haas is professor of sociology at the University of Amsterdam. He is a founding member and a former director of the International Migration Institute at the University of Oxford. He is also extraordinary professor of migration and development at the University of Maastricht/United Nations University. More information on his research and publications can be found on www.heindehaas.org.
</description>
